ayered world that reacts to scroll. It’s subtle, but powerful — turning static sections into dynamic experiences.p>\n        <p data-underline-link=\"\" class=\"demo-eyebrow\">Scroll down ↓p>\n      div>\n      <div class=\"demo-header__col\">\n        <img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68ecabe37c9bd7423c65df4e/68ecc45be5d83f026c6c91d5_Freshly%20Baked%20Bread.avif\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"Bread\" class=\"demo-header__img\">\n      div>\n    div>\n  section>\n  <div data-footer-parallax=\"\" class=\"footer-wrap\">\n    <footer data-footer-parallax-inner=\"\" class=\"demo-footer\">\n      <div class=\"demo-footer__links-row\">\n        <div class=\"demo-footer__col\">\n          <p class=\"demo-eyebrow\">( Pages )p>\n          <div class=\"demo-footer__links\">\n            <a data-underline-link=\"\" href=\"#\" class=\"demo-footer__a\">Homea>\n            <a data-underline-link=\"\" href=\"#\" class=\"demo-footer__a\">Resourcesa>\n            <a data-underline-link=\"\" href=\"#\" class=\"demo-footer__a\">Abouta>\n            <a data-underline-link=\"\" href=\"#\" class=\"demo-footer__a\">Platforma>\n            <a data-underline-link=\"\" href=\"#\" class=\"demo-footer__a\">Logina>\n          div>\n        div>\n        <div class=\"demo-footer__col\">\n          <p class=\"demo-eyebrow\">( Socials )p>\n          <div class=\"demo-footer__links\">\n            <a data-underline-link=\"\" href=\"#\" class=\"demo-footer__a\">LinkedIna>\n            <a data-underline-link=\"\" href=\"#\" class=\"demo-footer__a\">Instagrama>\n            <a data-underline-link=\"\" href=\"#\" class=\"demo-footer__a\">X/Twittera>\n          div>\n        div>\n        <div class=\"demo-footer__col\">\n          <p class=\"demo-eyebrow\">( Contact )p>\n          <div class=\"demo-footer__links\">\n            <a data-underline-link=\"\" href=\"#\" class=\"demo-footer__a\">hello@mukta.supplya>\n            <a data-underline-link=\"\" href=\"#\" class=\"demo-footer__a\">+31 6 12 